@startuml UC5_HighLevel_Handle_Predictive_Maintenance_Alert
title UC5 — Handle Predictive Maintenance Alert (High-Level)

skinparam Style strictuml
autonumber

actor "IoT Sensors" as IoT
participant "Maintenance Management System" as MMS
participant "Notification Service" as Notif
actor Supervisor

IoT -> IoT : Detect abnormal sensor reading
IoT -> MMS : Send abnormal sensor reading

MMS -> MMS : Validate sensor data
MMS -> MMS : Perform threshold checking\nand predictive diagnostics
MMS -> MMS : Store sensor alert
MMS -> MMS : Create predictive maintenance request

MMS -> Notif : Send predictive maintenance request notification
Notif -> Supervisor : Notify predictive maintenance request

MMS --> IoT : Confirm reading accepted

@enduml